immutable_data.name: Hold Ur Head Up
immutable_data.description: Cment Global LLC "Hold Ur Head Up" single collection. Each purchase of the NFT during the production period will entitle the owner to the following:  One FREE download of the music single “Hold Ur Head Up” from Charlie & Friends.  Exclusive access to an INVITATION ONLY online screening and behind the scenes interview with the cast of the Romantic Comedy production of “Tha Referee”.  NFT owners who are active in the “Hold Ur Head Up” Telegram Messenger chat group at the time of production will appear in the credits as Associate Producers at the end of the movie “Tha Referee” either as the (“Hold Ur Head Up” Telegram Group) or individually named, at the discretion of the Executive Production staff.  *Terms subject to change as required by law.
